\s UHORAHO TURAGUSHIMIYE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Uhoraho turagushimiye kubw’igikorwa cawe kubw’imigambi yawe Uhoraho Mana, turagushimiye kubw’ijambo ryawe, Manu yanyegejwe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uhoraho Ur’Imana, Imana yihisha uwo itihishuriye ntashobora kukumenya uwo wihishuriye asanga uko wari ejo ariko uri uyu munsi kandi ariko uzokwama ibihe bidashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Turagushimiye ko watwihishuriye ukaturongoza inkingi y’umuriro ukaduha manu nsha y’igihe cacu niryo jambo ryawe, Jambo rihishuwe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uhoraho Ur’Imana, Imana yihisha uwo itihishuriye ntashobora kukumenya uwo wihishuriye asanga uko wari ejo ariko uri uyu munsi kandi ariko uzokwama ibihe bidashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Wakuye Isirayeli, muri Egiputa ni wewe warirongoye mu bugaragwa kandi ni wewe warishikanye I Kanani kuko wewe ur’Imana, Imana y’bushobozi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uhoraho Ur’Imana, Imana yihisha uwo itihishuriye ntashobora kukumenya uwo wihishuriye asanga uko wari ejo ariko uri uyu munsi kandi ariko uzokwama ibihe bidashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ku murango w’abarongoza igicu mw’ijoro ukabarongoza inkingi y’umuriro bashonje wabagaburira manu nsha kuko wewe uri Imana, Imana y’urukundo\bd*
\pc \bdit Uhoraho Ur’Imana, Imana yihisha uwo itihishuriye ntashobora kukumenya uwo wihishuriye asanga uko wari ejo ariko uri uyu munsi kandi ariko uzokwama ibihe bidashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nkuko washikanye Isirayeli I Kanani natwe tur’ingenzi tugiye I Siyoni twizeye kuzodushikana imuhira kuko wewe ur’Imana, idahindagurika.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uhoraho Ur’Imana, Imana yihisha uwo itihishuriye ntashobora kukumenya uwo wihishuriye asanga uko wari ejo ariko uri uyu munsi kandi ariko uzokwama ibihe bidashira.\bdit*
